Rumble looked up to Soundwave and sighed, as Spasstik finished growling,
and followed Frenzy, taking a step back, then using the momentum to leap
up and transform, neatly entering Soundwave. Rumble wanted some kind of
action after so many years of imprisonment. He had waited for three
hundred years, he wasnt looking forward to waiting any longer. He took a
step forward to leap up, and transformed, but stopped, and listened
carefully. 

"Soun, Soundwave, you hear that?" he asked cheerfully. "It's someone
who's looking for some Decepticons. Let me and Frenzy go meet him."
Rumble said, demanding instead of asking, as he looked up to the large
Decepticon Comunicator.
